items.title: Reds prospect Greene to stick with pitching

items.title: Roberts: We're trying to get that swagger back
items.summary: Remember when the Dodgers were in the midst of a historic slide, opening the door for the Nationals to overtake them for the National League's best record? Consider that door closed.
